casebody.data:
Monday, December 14, 1998

DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

98-1758. Disciplinary Counsel v. Fish.

Upon consideration of respondent’s motion to withdraw objections,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to withdraw objections be, and hereby is, granted.

IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that oral argument currently scheduled for December 16,1998, be canceled.
